### 1. Login - Obtener Token
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
    client.log("Token guardado: " + response.body.token);
%}

### 2. Login con credenciales incorrectas (debería fallar)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrong"
}

### 3. Acceder a endpoint protegido CON token
GET http://localhost:8080/videos/getAll
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 4. Acceder a endpoint protegido SIN token (debería fallar)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/videos

### 5. Acceder con token inválido (debería fallar)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/videos
Authorization: Bearer token-falso

### 6. Probar otro endpoint protegido
POST http://localhost:8080/api/videos
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Video",
  "description": "Testing with JWT"
}
